items.description:
Support needed ! Out of colab credits. You can support me here to be able to render better models (https://ko-fi.com/djo226). Supporters can request model.

You can also subscribe to my Patreon and get exclusive models like this one (Jinx, Velma, Lara Croft, ...) .

Jessica Rabbit is a fictional character in the novel Who Censored Roger Rabbit? and its film adaptation, Who Framed Roger Rabbit. She is depicted as Roger's human toon wife in various Roger Rabbit media. Jessica is renowned as one of the best-known sex symbols in animation. She is also well-known for the line: "I'm not bad, I'm just drawn that way."

Prompt : a woman, realistic, natural lighting, post-processing, ultra realistic, highly detailed, very detailed, cinematic, hyper realistic, intricate scenery, sharp, photo by Annie Leibovitz, film, studio lighting, detailed skin, ultra realistic, bokeh, sharp features <lora:Rabbit:0.6>

Use a woman as trigger. Normaly, it should be Rabbit, but it gives a rabbit or Jessica with bunny hears.

items.name: Persephanii
items.description:
Persephanii (Stephanie Nelson) is an American model.

Training includes, well, a lot of cleavage. Can get nsfw. You may want to use "(nude:2)" or something similar as a negative prompt.

She is known as the "thick yonce". You could experiment with keyword blending to tweak her facial features (e.g. "[p3rs3phan11:Beyoncé:0.9]"). Other ways to tweak her look include the Hyperbreast LoRa and the Gigantomastia Hypernetwork.

Under some setups, this embedding can create a glaring color scheme. This can usually be fixed, though, (for example, with epi_noiseoffset). She likes to wear blue by default.

See more pictures of her on my DeviantArt page.

items.name: Futura Silver
items.description:
My rating vs expectation: 95%

(Very happy with this result. See TIPS to get the most out of it. See "about this version" for changes. This is the final version for Silver.)

All TIs I make depict real adults. Please apply it with good judgement. If you're the model and want this removed reach out to me via link below. I welcome all criticisms and suggestions with curiosity. If you like my work, buy me a house:
https://ko-fi.com/futurafree

This TI was trained in sd1.5 base with 5 vectors, 26 images, 12200 steps, and 469 epochs. This was finetuned for epiCRealism evo3 and Realistic Vision V4.0, but may work on others.

TIPS:

  • MUST be the first word in the prompt for likeness and consistency.

    • Example: futurasilver12200v52, portrait of a woman, long dress etc.

    • Not: Portrait of futurasilver12200v52, etc.

  • Recommended strength:

    • (0.98-1.0)

  • I use adetailer for all images, with mediapipe_face_full, blank pos and neg, 1024x1024, inpaint mask blur: 20, inpaint noise strength: 0.45.

  • Again, prompt in adetailer is left blank most of the time; (*exception*: if Loras/Lycoris is used and has significant impact on the appearance of the model's face, copy paste pos prompt without Loras/Lycoris into adetailer).

  • Upscaler I use: 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.

天若有情天亦老，老子也是冬马党。

大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次给大家带来的是东马和纱人物lora。

值得一提的是，这次的人物lora并不是完全还原原作，因为我的训练集不都是白色相簿2的cg图，不得不说十年前的gal图cg那个画风在今天看实在是有些过时了，训练集里有很多是p站上的同人图，然而东马的同人图格外的少，所以我还放了一些用之前深崎暮人lora重绘的动画截图（没错，我训练深崎暮人lora就为了这个，属于是为了这点醋包的饺子），然后我还加入了一些鬼月的御姐图，虽然听起来这俩完全不沾边，但是我隐约觉得鬼月的御姐脸型放在东马身上肯定不违和，于是便训练出了这个lora。画风我还是很满意的，是我很喜欢的脸型，并且还保留了原有人物的那种神韵（不过这个就见仁见智了）。

然后我训练的时候脑子抽了，忘记删掉black hair和blue eyes这俩tag了，导致每次写的时候都得加上这俩才能保证出东马，否则头发颜色会不对。然后可以画一些和雪菜的贴贴图，例图中那几个我是用ctrlnet的softedge模式引导做出的。

Well, for some reason there is still no image information, so I added a compressed package of the sample image to the file,you can try to read the picture information yourself,hoping that this will not go wrong again.)

20230721更新：

20230721 updates:

流光溢彩组合 ✧*｡ (ˊᗜˋ*) ✧*｡

大概的思路啦：通过调整提示词的权重之间，让画面渐渐变的可控。

通常我会使用的正面提示词是（masterpiece,best quality,），以及会在负面提示词中添加的（lowres,bad anatomy,bad hands,text,error,missing fingers,extra digit,fewer digits,cropped,worst quality,low quality,normal quality,jpeg artifacts,signature,watermark,username,blurry,bad feet）,使用这些会帮助你的画面更加精美，使人物肢体更加合理。但是！这些提示词只是在基本情况下使用，如果想要不同的效果还是需要调整的哦（比如在流光溢彩组合里，添加的彩虹效果很容易就会变成儿童绘画里的卡通彩虹,这样的效果当然不是我们想要的啦，所以这时候需要在负面提示词中添加 children's illustration,cartoon rainbow painting之类的提示词）

  • 首先画面中十分明显的的分布一些要素（阳光的散射效果，彩虹色的光影，多彩的瞳孔之类的），这些是实现虹彩效果的附加而控制效果的则是（,(strong emotions:1.1),(rainbow color:1.1),((tyndall effect)),(colorful pupils),(diffuse sunlight),iridescence pupils,iridescence hair,iridescence sunshine,）

  • 其次是画面镜头描述（正面描写，侧面描写，逆光之类的），这些效果可以进一步帮你确定最终画面的样式哦（,(upper body close-up:1.2),(side close-up:1.2,Backlight),）

  • 最后啦就是再对画面风格进行调整（梦幻，动态感一类的，同时这一步也可以使用Lora来帮助确定风格）（,(((fantasy))),(dream),(yoneyamamai style),）

Tips:最后的最后啦，任何一种风格的提示词都是一点一点调整出来的，就像这样:

1.

2.

3.

4.

可以发现啦，在每一阶段图片的效果都是有所不同的，甚至是第一张图和最后的效果完全无关的情况，这都是很正常的事情，在不断调整提示词和提示词的权重的过程中慢慢让画面变成自己想要的样子，我写提示词的想法也就是这样的啦。

还有还有，每一套提示词都是可以经过你的修改的，比如:

5.

当然啦，还可以和Lora相互结合哦，例如和我的v3.0模型相结合的效果:

6.

最后的最后的最后的啦，任何一套提示词都不是绝对保证效果的，它可能会被很多情况影响，比如使用的大模型不同，使用的生成比例不同之类的，都会影响最终的效果，所以也一定要知道不能被所谓的标准影响，需要由你自己慢慢尝试，找出适合你的那一种风格⊂(˃̶͈̀ε ˂̶͈́ ⊂ ).

希望每个人都能画出自己想要的画面啦，最后附上流光溢彩的提示词哦（,(((masterpiece))),(((best quality))),(((fantasy))),(blur background),(transparent blue eyes),hoodies,((upper body close-up:1.2)),(((midjourney))),((strong emotions)),shadow,(rainbow color:1.1),(after a storm comes a calm),iridescence pupils,(lovely:1.1),(white shirt:1.1),iridescence hair,(open your mouth:1.4),iridescence sunshine,knapsack,(flowing hair:1.1),(yoneyamamai style),(side close-up:1.2),(((raindrops in the air))),brilliant colors,fleshy skin,blue eyes,(well ventilated:1.1),((solo)),more detail,warm sunshine,iridescence sky,the sun shines down,(((facial polishing:1.1))),(laughing heartily),happy,dynamic feeling,blue sky,(colorful pupils),(diffuse sunlight),(( tyndall effect)),warm background,face to the side,((frontlighting)),）

值得一说的是流光溢彩除开使用了以上的提示词，还有使用了一些Lora(有梦幻世界的Lora以及我的另一个Lora模型，如果发现效果不太理想的话可以试着添加一些自己理想的Lora来帮助自己进一步固定风格！)

items.name: BiggerGirlsv5 / Bigger Girls v5 / BGV5 Lora Extract [Concept]
items.description:
A lora extract of the bigger girls v5 model against its base, the leaked novelai ckpt.

In theory, lets you use bigger girl sizes on any model. In practice, it does exactly that. More or less. Inpaints well enough.

Works fine at strength 1. Increasing strength makes girls go heavier and can do weirder concepts like "blob" or "immobile" better, but has a negative effect on composition, backgrounds, and general quality. Plays well with most loras, especially artist and character loras.

Can be tempermental when used on models or loras that already know fats- best used on normal models with no fat training.

Still requires biggergirls style prompting & settings. In a nutshell, use (high aesthetic, 1girl, solo:1.4) and clip skip 1 for best results.

Is a whopping 300 mb because lower dim sizes did not work at all. Maybe a higher dim would work even better? Something to try later.

Check out the bg discord & original civitai post for more information on biggergirls, such as tags or prompting, which will apply to this lora:

This model does a very good job at recreating the characters from Made in Abyss. The backgrounds are hit or miss, as most of the focus was on keeping characters usable. Now with 2GB pruned version!

Instructions from the authors of the original MIA model

Here's the text from the document reformatted for plaintext viewing on the internet. Note that this has been manually adjusted for readability, while maintaining the original content:

---

Link to discord server where we do training:

[Discord link]

Or you can add me directly on discord, 金Goldkoron#9929

I recommend using the following always as negative prompt:

lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry

(These are NovelAI's prompt template settings)

---

PROMPT FORMAT:

Character, tag1, tag2, etc; Character2, tag 1, tag2, etc; Location

(this is the format the model is trained with, it's not necessary but recommended for best results)

Explanation for this prompt format: Commas separate subtags for a major concept or character while semicolons act as major concept separators for generating multiple characters or marking the location at end of prompt.

EXAMPLES:

1. Riko, shift dress, red whistle; orphanage

2. Riko, delver outfit, delver helmet, red whistle; Reg, aubade helmet, aubade cape, backpack; the forest of temptation

3. Riko, delver outfit, red whistle; Reg, aubade helmet, aubade cape, arm extended; the inverted forest, seeker camp

items.description:
An experimental character LoRA of Pola from Kantai Collection.

Info

Training with 215 images
Followed the manual form [ [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free ],
You can access to this guide in Suggested Resources section.

Recommended set up

Sampler: Euler a, DPM family series
Sampling steps: 20 or 25+
CFG Scale: 7
CLIP Skip: 2
*Do not use [restore face] on anime character!*

LoRA Weighting: [1 - 0.8], (1 - 0.7)

Baking Step:
0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

Upscaler for [Step 1 - 3]: [R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp]
I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

Basic prompts

PolaKC, (long sleeves) shirt, (white) shirt, (white) corset, frills, bodice, (red) bowtie, (red) miniskirt, (white) thighhighs, (mini) hat, tilted headwear, boots
-(off shoulder:1.5) !NEG!

Irish style interior design draws on the country's rich history, natural beauty, and cultural traditions to create warm, inviting, and character-filled spaces. It's known for its blend of rustic charm and timeless elegance, capturing the essence of both rural and urban Ireland.

The color palette often takes cues from the Irish landscape, incorporating hues of green, blue, gray, and earth tones. Traditional materials like wood, stone, and wool are frequently used, symbolizing a connection to the land and local craftsmanship.

Furniture tends to be sturdy and functional, with pieces often made from solid wood and displaying quality craftsmanship. Elements such as exposed wooden beams, stone fireplaces, and vintage items are common features, adding a sense of history and authenticity.

Decorative accents might include Irish lace, crystal, hand-woven textiles, or pottery. Irish design often includes a touch of whimsy as well, perhaps through the use of playful patterns or nods to folklore.

items.name: Indian style interior design
items.description:
Only for SD 2.1

Indian style interior design is characterized by its rich colors, intricate patterns, and a wealth of detailed craftsmanship. It draws inspiration from India's diverse cultural heritage, regional traditions, and historical influences.

The color palette typically includes vibrant hues like deep red, mustard yellow, and royal blue, often contrasted with gold or silver accents. Materials commonly used include wood, metal, and rich textiles such as silk, cotton, and wool.

Indian furniture is known for its ornate carvings, inlaid designs, and colorful upholstery. Low seating arrangements, carved wooden divans, and heavy wooden chests are common. Decorative elements can include anything from intricate brass or terracotta sculptures, to embroidered cushions, to richly detailed rugs and draperies.

Architectural features often include large, open spaces, arched doorways, and ornate window designs. Elements such as jharokhas (traditional Indian balconies), jaali (latticed screens), and richly decorated ceilings can also be found.

Overall, Indian style interior design is about creating an extravagant, opulent, and vibrant environment, filled with the warmth and richness of Indian culture.
